The Keiser Report  No. 235
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 12 January 2012


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy discuss death by a thousand revelations and destroying the City to save the City. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to author, Nomi Prins, a former investment banker, about the role of JP Morgan in Jon Corzine's MF Global crime.
